{"tid":365155,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"傷心通粉","createTime":"2017-08-19T04:34:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T04:43:22.000Z","uid":106307,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"39f7ebeb4af50324fe9f23a9d66a4270b269d539","tid":365155,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:34:23.000Z","msg":"剛與最愛的女人分開，心，很痛。<br />\n<br />\n她，曾經跟我說，想我早餐不要吃即食麵，改吃通粉。往後的日子，我的早餐，便再沒有即食麵的出現。而每一次，我也會拍一張照片，告訴她，告訴自己，我，有重視和記得她的說話。<br />\n<br />\n如今，我再吃不下通粉，分手後，我嘗試叫一碗通粉。但，我呆呆的看著那碗通粉，眼水不自覺便會盈滿眼眶，在家如是，在餐廳亦如是......<br />\n<br />\n原來，面對最愛的回憶，是這麼的痛苦。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n營多麼需要你......我會罷吃通粉了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b96dd6ca86e3332d3d9d3cefc2725580e2900ea","tid":365155,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:43:22.000Z","msg":"誰偷偷留下負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}